Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia an shirya shi ne don karfe bakwai na dare a yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a karkashin watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron wannan makon game da nadin Burt Kavanaugh zuwa Kotun Koli inda ake ta daɗaɗaɗa kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i, kuma an jinkirta zaben Majalisar Dattawa na kwanaki bakwai har sai FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu nasara a zaben watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, daga yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa Trump sun ce taron na wannan makon yana da nufin ba da makamashi ga masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da faɗaɗa rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Dattijai, a cewar rahoton Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a majalisar wakilai na da muhimmanci sosai a cikin tsarinsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda ya kamata yayin da muke shiga kakar yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin Trump ga Reuters wanda ya ki bayyana kansa.
An shirya taron a Westbanco Arena a Wheeling, wanda zai iya tara magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania a yau kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, a cewar wani labari na West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne zai zama karo na biyu da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a wannan watan, jihar da ya lashe gasar da sama da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana ƙoƙarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican daga West Virginia, wanda ba ya da kyau a cikin binciken.
"Ba wata alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya yi ƙoƙarin ƙara darajarsa a cikin binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar rahoton Reuters.
