Turai ta ci gaba da kaiwa 10:6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta shiga gasar Ryder ta karshe da babbar nasara, bayan wasan Asabar da aka yi a wasan da aka yi da balls hudu da fours, ta samu nasara 10:6 a kan Amurka.
Matar da ta yi wahayi zuwa gare ta, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari, sun jagoranci farko da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods mai rashin jin daɗi, wanda ya kara yawan abin da aka samu a filin wasa na Le Golf National da maki hudu.
'Yan Turai na Thomas Bjørn suna gwagwarmaya don dawo da kyautar da suka yi a gidan golf na Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, sun mamaye 'yan Amurka marasa daidaito a wasan safiya na hudu kuma sun lashe wasan da kashi daya zuwa uku.
Amurka ta fi tsayayya da gasar ta hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage baya ba.
A ranar Lahadi, 'yan wasan Jim Fury za su ci maki takwas a wasanni 12 da suka buga domin su ci gaba da lashe kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya fara samun maki hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, da ake kira Molliwood bayan kyakkyawan karshen mako, kawai ma'aurata biyu ne a tarihin Ryder Cup da suka ci maki hudu a farkon wasanni huɗu.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan da aka buga da balls hudu, sun yi nasara sosai a kan wani matashi mai ƙarancin ƙarfi da Woods da kuma ɗan wasan farko na Amurka, Bryson DeCambeau, da kuma karin nasara 5:4.
Woods wanda ya yi nasara a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi kyau a wasu lokutan, amma yanzu ya yi asara 19 daga cikin 29 a wasan da balls hudu da hudu da kuma bakwai a jere.
Jason Rose, wanda ya yi hutu a wasan safiya da ƙwallon ƙafa huɗu, ya koma abokin aikinsa Henry Stenson a gasar huɗu kuma ya sha kashi 2:1 a gaban Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepke, na farko da na uku a duniya.
Amma ba duk abin da ya faru a Turai ba ne a wannan rana mai kyau a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, sun yi nasara a gasar cin kofin Amurka da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
