HIV/AIDS: Sin ta samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta ce an samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 a yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka ji rauni a ƙasar, in ji jami'an lafiya.
An yi rahoton sababbin mutane 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kawai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka suna faruwa ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da yadda suke a dā.
A dā, cutar HIV ta yi sauri a wasu sassan ƙasar Sin don ta kamu da jini da aka yi masa.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya kusan raguwa, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
Tun daga shekara ta 1997, ba a ƙara la'akari da cin zarafin 'yan luwadi a kasar Sin ba, amma an ce nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi a duniya ya zama ruwan dare.
Wasu bincike sun nuna cewa saboda ra'ayoyin masu ra'ayin mazan jiya a kasar nan, maza 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 da suke yin jima'i da maza suna zuwa auren mata.
Sau da yawa, ana iya samun kamuwa da cutar ta wajen rashin kariya ta jima'i a irin wannan yanayin.
A shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da maganin HIV a duniya a matsayin wani ɓangare na shirin magance wannan matsalar.
